---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
    <main class="p-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto text-aura-deep dark:text-aura-cream bg-aura-soft dark:bg-aura-deep rounded-2xl shadow">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-aura-green dark:text-aura-yellow mb-4">Collaborators</h1>

        <p class="mb-4">
            The AURA Protocol is an open and collaborative effort driven by experts in artificial intelligence,
            scientific reproducibility, and digital ethics. It brings together researchers, developers, and educators
            committed to promoting transparency and accountability in the use of generative AI.
        </p>

        <div class="mb-6">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-aura-leather dark:text-aura-yellow mb-2">Lead Contributor:</h2>
            <p>
                <strong>Dr. Fausto David Cortes Rojas</strong> – Researcher and professor in Biomedical Engineering,
                with specialization in AI transparency, image processing, and ethical applications of generative models.
                He has authored peer-reviewed publications and led interdisciplinary research projects at the
                intersection of technology and medicine.
            </p>
            <ul class="text-sm text-aura-green dark:text-aura-yellow mt-2 space-y-1 ml-4 list-disc list-inside">
                <li>
                    <a href="https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5224-5710" class="hover:text-aura-leather dark:hover:text-aura-cream" target="_blank">ORCID Profile</a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href="https://www.webofscience.com/wos/author/record/MFI-2232-2025" class="hover:text-aura-leather dark:hover:text-aura-cream" target="_blank">Web of Science Author Record</a>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-6">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-aura-leather dark:text-aura-yellow mb-2">Contributing Technologies:</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4">
                <li>OpenAI API – GPT-based generation used during protocol drafting</li>
                <li>Astro Framework – Site development and deployment</li>
                <li>Tailwind CSS – Styling and responsive design</li>
                <li>GitHub – Version control and collaboration</li>
                <li>Vercel – Deployment and hosting</li>
                <li>AWS – Cloud storage and API services</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <p class="mt-6 text-sm text-aura-sepia dark:text-aura-olive italic">
            Interested in contributing to the protocol, suggesting improvements, or joining the initiative?
            Reach out via <a href="mailto:fdavid.cortezr@cinvestav.mx" class="hover:text-aura-leather dark:hover:text-aura-cream">email</a> or submit proposals on
            <a href="https://github.com/drfcortes/aura.org" class="hover:text-aura-leather dark:hover:text-aura-cream">GitHub</a>.
        </p>
    </main>
</Layout>
